data.description:
Nestled in the heart of a serene neighborhood, this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. With a high ceiling and a loft that adds character and dimension, this home is a true gem. Welcome to your dream home!
Additionally, this home features a 2-car garage, providing ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. The unfinished basement offers the potential for further customization or additional living space, making it an excellent opportunity for future expansion.

This property is perfectly located near the picturesque Cherry Creek State Park, providing endless opportunities for outdoor activities and recreation. Enjoy hiking, biking, water sports, and picnics in this beautiful natural setting, all just moments from your doorstep.

This home is not just a place to live; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make it yours. Contact us today to schedule a showing and discover the endless possibilities this home has to offer. Your new adventure begins here!
